com.hybris.cis.client.rest.common.mock

Class ThirdPartyRequestSimulationAspect

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hybris.cis.client.rest.common.mock.ThirdPartyRequestSimulationAspect
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean

    public class ThirdPartyRequestSimulationAspect
extends Object
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean

    Simulates outbound third party request calls to Cybersource, Avalara, UPS and other CIS vendors.

    This is implemented as an aspect to run after all public methods matching the following pointcut expression:
    com.hybris.cis.api..service.*ServiceMockImpl.*

        public void processDelay()
